<br>
I got tired of asking for assistance on the Fist of Earth, said fuck it, loaded my second computer, and went after him.  My monk is level 63, had 1200 AC and 3007 HP buffed by my 60 shaman (no Aegolism, KEI or enchanter haste); using Krag's Mending and Canni IV, Trunt died with my my monk at 100% health, and shaman at 20% health, 2% mana.<br>
<br>
(Trunt runs at approximately 20% health, which really, really helped.)<br>
<br>
So, he's a wuss.  Would not recommend doing what I did; it was an extremely stupid move, born of frustration.  But it is possible.<br>
<br>
